name: "Psychedelic Beast" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Various pens on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and mega-moshing.] As the "Let It Be" beastie appeared in our reality, a splinter of the cosmos caught on one of the beast's toe-claws and caused a bit of a tear in the space-time fabric. Naturally, this lead to a strange ripple effect that created (or allowed in) ANOTHER strange creature...  ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
